http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Woman-daughter-stuck-in-lift/article13986955.ece

A woman and her two-year-old daughter were stuck in the lift of their apartment building in HSR Layout for more an hour on Thursday morning.Other residents of Srinivasa Vaibava Apartments on Sarjapur Road heard Bhanu (27) shouting for help.They called the security guard. After failing to rescue Bhanu and her daughter Ishani, they alerted the fire control room.Fire personnel rushed to the spot after receiving a call around 9.30 a.m.Preliminary investigations revealed that the lift got stuck on the fourth floor due to a snag. Senior officials of the Fire and Emergency Services Department said that residents have been advised to get the lift repaired and ensure regular maintenance.